snippet.title: Skin Condition, Plastic Surgery, Or Makeup? Demystifying The Bruises On Amber Heard's Face.
snippet.description:
In the comment section of the last video I did  some people suggested or wondered if it were possible that Amber Heard either had or was passing off a skin condition as bruises. In this video I seek to demystify whether this is true or not and to also explore the possibility that the bruises could be from plastic surgery. Lastly, I revisit the possibility that the bruises are actually makeup. 

In the end, you be the judge on whether the so called bruises on Heard's face are some sort of skin condition, plastic surgery, or makeup.
